{"word":"ἀπεργασία","slug":"ἀπεργασία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπεργασία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀπεργάζομαι'><el>ἀπεργάζομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a finishing off, completing</i>, of painters, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a making, producing</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>a business, trade</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}